    desc="Our Global Game Jam 2022 entry, I created the characters and weapon models in a low poly pixel art style and implemented the Mixamo animations."
    url="https://v3.globalgamejam.org/2022/games/honourable-dual-1"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div><!-- 2020 -->
  <HorizontalCard
    title="Supa Happy Deth Slide"
    img="/gmtk20_thumb.webp"
    subtitle="UE4, 2020"
